column5: Came across this site. Theres some realy cool stuff here  http://www.irelandsantiquefishingtackle.com/
Excellent find Brian Love that old stuff, it was made to last forever

Just nice to see the old stuff Paul. I see there are a few cardnals that are going for a fair price.Even though it,s in pounds.  Also, you see that the pin reels were evented way back,with drag.Pretty cool.

I know, i threw an old cardinal in the trash a few years ago. Back when i thought i would never fish again I have some old stuff from my Dad and Grandfather.I keep sayiing i'm gonna clean them up and use them at least once, but i never get around to it
